To build adatoccpptranslator:
_ set CPP environment variable with g++ path
_ set YACC environment variable with bison path
_ set LEX environment variable with flex path
_ to build the translator execute command: make

g++ should be at least g++ 3.2
flex should be at least 2.5.2
bison should be at least 1.24

Adatoccpptranslator can be build under Linux, Cygwin, Windows ( by using MinGw32)
